  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a continental buffet breakfast each morning, from 7.30-10am, in the Panorama Room. You'll also have the option to order additional hot items, like bacon and eggs, from the menu (pay locally). The evening meal is four courses, with a choice of main and is also served in the Panorama Room from 6-9pm.</p>
<p>The hotel has two a la carte restaurants (pay locally). B<span>ü</span>nder <span>Stübli is a traditional restaurant, serving typical Swiss cuisine - it's a great choice for a special occasion or romantic candlelit meal. Casetta Allegra is the hotel's other a la carte restaurant, at the children's bowling alley - they serve delicious raclette. </span></p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
