  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Rooms</strong> have been newly renovated in a modern, warm alpine style with wooden flooring. They are about 25m² and sleep up to three (extra single bed). </p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> are around 35m² and sleep up to four people (extra single bed or bunk beds). These rooms have a double bedroom as well as a smaller room with bunk beds for children. Renovated Family Room Superior are available for a supplement, they have ben decorated in a modern, warm alpine style with wooden flooring. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are around 12.5m² sleeping one with a single bed.  These rooms typically have a balcony or seating area.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Minibar/minifridge </li>
<li>Most rooms have a balcony however this is not guaranteed</li>
<li>Kettle</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safety deposit box </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Cots are available on request</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
